      <text xml:space="preserve">{{other uses}}
{{Infobox Monarch
| name = King Ahab
| title = [[Kingdom of Israel (Samaria)|King of Israel]]
| image = [[File:Ahab rex.jpg|200px]]
| caption = Ahab from &quot;Promptuarii Iconum Insigniorum&quot;
| reign = c. 869 &amp;ndash; 850 BC
| coronation =  
| predecessor = [[Omri]] 
| successor = [[Ahaziah of Israel]]
| suc-type =
