The following list is partially based on [http://www.bu.edu/english/levine/alcend.htm an overview by Robert Levine and Whitney Bolton]

;Poetry
*''Carmina'', ed. Ernst Dümmler. ''Poetae Latini Aevi Carolini''. vol 1. Berlin, 1881.
