** [[Robert of Molesme]]
** [[Torpes of Pisa]]
** [[April 29 (Eastern Orthodox liturgics)]]
* [[International Dance Day]] ([[International observance|International]])
* [[Koninginnedag#Queen.27s_Night|Queen's Night]] (the [[Netherlands]])
* [[Shōwa Day]], traditionally the start of the [[Golden Week (Japan)|Golden Week]] holiday period. ([[Japan]])
* The beginning of [[Arita, Saga|Arita Ceramic Fair]] ([[Arita, Saga]], [[Japan]])
* The ninth day of [[Ridván]] ([[Bahá'í Faith]])

