*  1984   &amp;ndash; [[Robin Söderling]], Swedish tennis player
*[[1985]] &amp;ndash; [[Christian Gentner]], German footballer
*  1985   &amp;ndash; [[Shea Weber]], Canadian hockey player
*[[1986]] &amp;ndash; [[Terin Humphrey]], American gymnast
*[[1987]] &amp;ndash; [[James Buckley (actor)|James Buckley]], English actor
*  1987    &amp;ndash; [[Tim Tebow]], American football player and winner of 2007 Heisman trophy
*  1987   &amp;ndash; [[Chrystina Sayers]], American singer and dancer ([[Girlicious]])
*[[1988]] &amp;ndash; [[Shahd Barmada]], Syrian singer
*[[1989]] &amp;ndash; [[Kyle Turris]], Canadian ice hockey player
*[[1990]] &amp;ndash; [[Jaydee Bixby]], Canadian singer

