* [[Wigger (river)|Wigger]]
* [[Emme (river)|Emme]]
* [[Zihlkanal]]
** [[Suze (river)|Suze]]
** [[Broye]]
** [[Orbe (river)|Orbe]]
* [[Saane]] (Sarine)
** [[Sense (river)|Sense]]
* [[Kander]]
** [[Simme]]
** [[Allenbach]]
* [[Lütschine]]

