      <comment>what Islam says about A, with citation</comment>
      <text xml:space="preserve">{{About|the biblical Abraham}}
{{Infobox saint
|name=Abraham
|birth_date=1948 [[Anno Mundi]] (early second millennium BCE)
|death_date=
|feast_day=
|venerated_in=[[Judaism]]&lt;br&gt;[[Christianity]]&lt;br&gt;[[Islam]]&lt;br&gt;[[Mandaeism]]&lt;br&gt;[[Baha'i Faith]]
