|titles=Prophet, Seer, First Hebrew Patriarch, Father of the Multitude, Holy Forefather, ''[[Ḥanīf]]'', ''Friend of God''&lt;!-- This last title is accorded in the Qur'an as ''Khalil-Allah'' --&gt;, 'Possessor of Power and Vision'&lt;!-- This last title is accorded in the Qur'an --&gt;, Constructor of the [[Kaaba]], Abraham the Kind&lt;!-- This last description is given in the Qur'an --&gt;
