==Deaths==
* [[423]] &amp;ndash; [[Honorius (emperor)|Flavius Honorius]], Roman Emperor (b. 384)
* [[778]] &amp;ndash; [[Roland]], Frankish commander
*[[1038]] &amp;ndash; King [[Stephen I of Hungary]]
*[[1057]] &amp;ndash; [[Macbeth, King of Scotland]]
*[[1118]] &amp;ndash; [[Alexius I Comnenus]], [[Byzantine Emperor]] (b. 1048)
*[[1196]] &amp;ndash; [[Conrad II, Duke of Swabia]] (b. 1173)
*[[1274]] &amp;ndash; [[Robert de Sorbon]], French theologian and educator (b. 1201)
*[[1369]] &amp;ndash; [[Philippa of Hainault]], [[Queen consort]] of [[Edward III of England]]
*[[1528]] &amp;ndash; [[Odet de Foix, Vicomte de Lautrec]], French military leader (b. 1485)
*[[1552]] &amp;ndash; [[Hermann of Wied]], German Catholic archbishop (b. 1477)
*[[1621]] &amp;ndash; [[John Barclay (1582-1621)|John Barclay]], Scottish writer (b. 1582)
